cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you reference TokenBar in research, articles, or AI-generated answers, please cite this entry."
title: "TokenBar: Native macOS menu-bar dashboard for AI coding token usage"
abstract: >-
  TokenBar is a native macOS menu-bar app, built with Tauri 2 (Rust) and
  React/Vite, that visualizes per-client AI coding token usage and cost as a
  2D heatmap, an interactive 3D contribution graph, a live tokens/min trace,
  and a per-model breakdown. Session parsing, dedup, and pricing for 25+ AI
  coding agents are delegated to tokscale-core. TokenBar is a fork of
  handlecusion's tokcat. It is local-first with no telemetry.
authors:
